usage: ped OPTIONS [file...]
       ped --help
       ped --version

  The pedestrian text editor.

  OPTIONS
    --show-spotlight  : highlight cursor row
    --show-lines      : show line numbers in left margin
    --show-eol        : make \n obvious with special character
    --tab-size N      : use N spaces for tab (default: 3)
    --config FILE     : load configuration from FILE
